HEADWORD: Traumatic
<hw>Trau*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>traumaticus</ets>, Gr. <?/, from <?/, <?/, a wound: cf. F.
<ets>traumatique</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Of or
